Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.41,0:00:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Barian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barian?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say you're Barian?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I came here in order to annihilate Astral World,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the messenger from Barian World!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Barian?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barian...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See for yourself!\NHeart-eartH Dragon's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this Monster with is destroyed while it has no Overlay Units,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be revived only once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:00:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The resurrected Heart-eartH Dragon's Attack Power increases
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:01:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by 1000 points for each card that has been Banished.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4000 Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, when Heart-eartH Dragon is Special Summoned successfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all Monsters on my opponent's field are switched to Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...Neo Galaxy-Eyes was...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too soon for you to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Continuous Spell, Barian's Gateway!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This turn, each time a card is sent to the Graveyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you will receive 800 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! We only have 100 of our Life left...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Heart-eartH Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.89,0:01:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Neo Galaxy-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heartbreak Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:01:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Trap! Photon Escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, when a Photon Monster is attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Banish that Monster and end the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have some strength left to struggle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, For every Banished card, Heart-eartH Dragon gains 1000 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5000 Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barian!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've come here to take Haruto away, just try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish things here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, HARUTO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Dimension Wanderer’s Monster Effect from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Monster is Banished, by sending this card from my hand to the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can inflict damage to my opponent equal to the total Attack Points of the Banished Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monsters I target are Shark Drake Weiss and Neo Galaxy-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, the total damage you receive is 7300 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I still had something like this up his sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my final strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryouga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this attack that transcends dimensions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Neo Galaxy-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Photon Stream!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Shark Drake Weiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depth Chaos Bite!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Very nice move, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate another effect of the Continuous Magic, Barian’s Gateway!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sending this card to the Graveyard, I can negate the opposing Monster’s effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He managed to avoid my strike?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaito! Are you alright? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sha-Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity. Now you're the only one left, Yuma Tsukumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, what scenery do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}awaits us on the other side of this hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, let's climb it together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too soon for us to turn back now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come to combine\N together the power dwelling inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta release my Soul Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running, keep running, until you get there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, once again, keep those challenges coming
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:06:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friends, keep on living in the here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep pressing onward together no matter what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your remaining Life is almost as good as gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention you don't have any Monsters on your field.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(456,506)}"Number 71: The Miraculous 'Bring it to 'Em'!\NOpen a Path to the Future, ZEXAL!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Yuma Tsukumo,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despair along with the Astral World!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all can just vanish into the depth of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! Not in a place like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma... Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma... Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always for my sake... For me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto… You little…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's using the power of Barian I gave him…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! The Sphere Field is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him see the power you share with Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma... Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I build the Overlay Network with the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When two distant souls intersect,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The generational force shall appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Change...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZEXAL!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power Yuma and Astral share with each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZEXAL!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are the force from Astral World, ZEXAL!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barian! Even if you stand in our way,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hope that shines within the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will defeat you along with the Bring it to 'em that burns inside my chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest Duelists can even choose the cards they draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the card of our destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SHINING DRAW!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon ZEXAL Weapon - Ultimate Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Ultimate Shield’s effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this card is Summoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By negating the effects of up to three Banished Xyz Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they can be Special Summoned in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revive! Chaos Number 39!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiring Emperor - Hope Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Integrate our power as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Chaos Number 32!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Drake Weiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be reborn, my very soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neo Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, because these three Banished Monsters have returned to the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart-eartH Dragon loses 3000 Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see? This is the true power of our combined strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just keep screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your end will not change!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sphere Field Cannon is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral may have escaped,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the Sphere Field Cannon already has enough energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot stop it now, no matter what you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can all just vanish together with the Astral World!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will leave everything to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I equip Hope Ray with Ultimate Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, Hope Ray gains 2000 Defense Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, I activate the Equip Magic, Xyz Unity, from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this card’s effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Ray is switched to Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then during this turn, Hope Ray gains Attack Points equal to the total Attack Power of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all Defense Position Monsters on my field!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, his Attack Power is now 9800!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Hope Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s useless! Regardless of how much you may have raised his Attack Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart-eartH Dragon is able to negate the battle damage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and bounce it back to all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate another effect of the Xyz Unity Equip Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I send Shark Drake Weiss to the Graveyard using this effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...allowing Hope Ray to attack once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...letting it attack you directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Permanent Trap, Barian's Battle Buster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Banishing a Barian card from my Graveyard, this card's effect
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,allows me to negate a Monster's attack up to twice per turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Banishing Barian's Gateway,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can negate your Direct Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch, I'm not done!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I send Neo-Galaxy Eyes to the Graveyard to attack once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...giving you another Direct Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish! I activate the effect of the Permanent Trap, Barian’s Battle Buster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Direct Attack is negated!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, by sending Barian’s Battle Buster to the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monsters on the field are forced to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! If Hope Ray battles as things are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6800 damage will bounce back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's {\i1}truly{\i0} over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Ultimate Shield’s effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this card is used as an Equip card, all Effect Damage is negated,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this card gains Attack Power equal to that amount of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, it negates all of Heart-eartH Dragon's effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible... Impossible... IMPOSSIBLE!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this attack worth 16600 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Hope Ray! Attack Heart-eartH Dragon and Barian!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Sword Ultimate Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you... bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that, Barian?! This is our bond!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of your nightmares have completely vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori! Kotori!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orbital! How long do you plan to keep sleeping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orbital Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orbital, take care of Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}, you aren't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will bring my dad back! I swear that I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori, take care of everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Yuma Tskumo? Why are you helping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be detestable...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you did your best to save Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any good father would shrug it off with a,\N "Can't be helped", and a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done enough, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have committed far too many sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should not be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have indeed committed too many sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YUMA!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron… Stop, Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your revenge is already over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Byron...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, Bryon.\N Kaito and the others have nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last... of my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s aright. It's gonna be alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Yuma always...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yo, Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma! Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you crying about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you really {\i1}are{\i0} an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always...{\i1}always{\i0} make me worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Byron...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Byron.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Faker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Byron.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Farewell, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you'd actually forgive me, Byron...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so reckless and keep pulling crazy stunts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean “it couldn’t be helped”?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's his spirit holding up, Droite?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already administered first aid, but we still must hurry, Gauche.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Gauche, Droite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Everything is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s all due to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Haruto, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuma, your heart that never gives up, and the trust you place in the bonds with your friends...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...has brought the light of hope back to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess the Duel Carnival is over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it‘s still not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven’t received my prize for winning the Duel Carnival!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa…wait… What are you saying at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner of the Duel Carnival is to be granted whatever wish they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And mine is for Kaito and his family to live together in happiness and in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}said{\i0} that it's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, alright, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, here's my {\i1}real{\i0} wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:22:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, you and I still haven’t settled the score yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can call this the {\i1}real{\i0} Final.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! I'm gonna bring it to ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.60,0:22:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on ahead, speeding up our throbbing beats
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen boys and girls, here's the secret to boys and girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really just so spontaneous, wild as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You might be a handful, but what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be up to no good, but learn for real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go the unpredictable route and shuffle your cards with a goal in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever you feel like you've lost your way, just take a minute to close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout "stop!" with all you've got, and there's your boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just stop here, not when we don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we get hurt, we can't just hesitate now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just give up, not when our future's a lot brighter than our today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriousness... It'll only make us keep fighting even harder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always get as fascinated as we want, and we'll fight on every day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.07,0:23:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final round of the World Duel Carnival is finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:23:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the true Final still hasn't started!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:23:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.66,0:24:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come to settle the score with our battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.21,0:24:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His strength is far greater than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel's making my chest throb with excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.04,0:24:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito... You aren't really...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Ultimate Showdown Has Come!!\N Yuma VS Kaito: The Other WDC Final!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.14,0:24:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean you can't Duel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.81,0:24:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal powers up this October!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.02,0:24:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A new enemy has come from the Barian World!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.90,0:24:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The title will be "Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal II!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.61,0:24:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It starts broadcasting October 7th, 5:30 PM!
